statements.statement:
SELECT DISTINCT
C1.cdf_meaning
FROM CODE_VALUE C1
WHERE C1.CODE_SET= 220 AND c1.cdf_meaning IN("FACILITY","BUILDING","NURSEUNIT","ROOM","BED","AMBULATORY")
order C1.cdf_meaning

SELECT DISTINCT C1.DISPLAY_KEY, c1.cdf_meaning, DESC=CNVTUPPER(C1.DESCRIPTION), /* C1.CODE_VALUE, */ C1.CODE_SET, C2.DISPLAY
FROM CODE_VALUE C1, CODE_VALUE_SET C2
PLAN C1 WHERE C1.CODE_SET= 220 AND C1.ACTIVE_IND= 1 and c1.cdf_meaning IN("FACILITY","BUILDING","NURSEUNIT","ROOM","BED","AMBULATORY") JOIN C2 WHERE C2.CODE_SET=c1.code_set
order C1.cdf_meaning, c1.display_KEY, DESC

templateDefinitions.name: CSM_ORD_L_ORDER_STATUS
templateDefinitions.definition: Order status is ORDER_STATUS. Order was canceled for the following reason: CANCEL_REASON
templateDefinitions.description: Template used to check the status of an order using the ORDER_EVENT. If status checked is "CANCELED" the Cancel Reason can also be checked.

statements.statement: SELECT cv.display FROM code_value cv WHERE cv.code_set = 6004 ORDER cv.display_key
SELECT cv.display FROM code_value cv WHERE cv.code_set = 1309

templateDefinitions.name: CSM_ORDER_CALLBACK
templateDefinitions.definition: Order service request CALLBACK with the priority PRIORITY link to LINK
templateDefinitions.description: Order a CSM callback service request with given priority.

statements.statement: SELECT concat( trim(C.CSM_CAT_DESC), " - ", trim(S.CSM_SUB_CAT_DESC)) FROM CSM_CATEGORIES C, CSM_SUB_CATEGORIES S, CSM_CAT_SUB_XREF R PLAN C WHERE C.CSM_CAT_ID > 0 JOIN S WHERE S.CSM_SUB_CAT_ID > 0 JOIN R WHERE R.CSM_CAT_ID = C.CSM_CAT_ID AND R.CSM_SUB_CAT_ID = S.CSM_SUB_CAT_ID AND R.CSM_CALLBACK_IND = 0 AND R.ACTIVE_IND = 0
select c.csm_prior_desc from csm_priorities c where c.csm_prior_id > 0 and c.csm_active_ind = 1
